headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: Coca-Cola's profitable brands have funded a growing dividend for 63 years.  AT&T generates repeat revenue from customers' monthly bills, making it a solid income investment.  If you're looking to boost your passive income, Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO) and AT&T (NYSE: T) are solid dividend stock choices right now.
